sequenceDiagram
  actor Owner
  participant Bot as Telegraf Bot
  participant Auth as Owner Check
  participant Handler
  participant Runner
  participant Session as Plan/Approval Session
  participant Executor

  Owner->>Bot: Send command or callback
  Bot->>Auth: Compare chat ID
  Auth-->>Bot: Authorized
  Bot->>Handler: Dispatch update
  Handler->>Runner: Run ask, agent, or plan workflow
  Runner->>Executor: Use tools and stage changes
  Runner->>Session: Store selection or approval state
  Session-->>Owner: Inline keyboard response
  Owner->>Bot: Select callback action
  Bot->>Session: Load session
  Session->>Executor: Apply or clear staging
